[Student "S"]
{Your top priority as responder is to show a Major suit if you have one, so you say 1\H. Partner jumps to 3\H.  

Partner knows you may have only 6 points and went to the 3-level anyway. He is inviting you to bid game if you have a bit more than the 6 you promised. You revalue up to 10 so you have quite a bit more. You accept his invitation and bid 4\H.}

